-- ============================================================================
-- Seed lookup catalogues from the DfE Common Basic Data Set (CBDS), version
-- May 2026. Replaces our earlier starter/curated seeds with the official lists
-- where a CBDS code set maps to one of our tables. CBDS becomes the source of
-- truth: each MERGE upserts the official rows (Active = 1), then any row NOT in
-- the CBDS set is deactivated (Active = 0) rather than deleted, so existing FK
-- references stay intact. Re-running is a no-op once converged.
--
-- Ids are deterministic (derived from table + code) so re-running is stable.
-- DisplayOrder is alphabetical by default (0); catch-all / "not stated" rows get
-- a high value so they sort below the list. Languages and Nationalities are pure
-- alphabetical (no DisplayOrder column). MaritalStatus has no CBDS code set, so it
-- keeps its existing seed.
-- ============================================================================

